item.title: CVE-2019-10460|2024-08-04T22:24:18.540Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20bitbucket%20oauth%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Bitbucket OAuth Plugin 0.9 and earlier stored credentials unencrypted in the global config.xml configuration file on the Jenkins master where they could be viewed by users with access to the master file system.
